Showcase::Common
================

Showcase::Common contains a number of components extracted from Showcase which
are suitable for reuse in other applications. At the moment, included in this
Gem are:

  Showcase::Common::Form
    A custom form builder which extends Merb's default. Adds support for
    date_field, time_field and datetime_field. Also included is a tweaked
    label which will add span.req around asterisks, and span.note around text
    which is in parenthesis.

  Showcase::Common::Nav
    Allows for easily building tabbed nevigation, selecting active tabs,
    linking to resources, and guarding tabs from those without sufficient
    permission.

  Showcase::Common::Masthead
    Creates the mastheads used in Showcase which contains the page title, and
    other various details.
